text: is a Japanese Olympian speed skater. == Education == Go is studying commerce at the Yamanashi Gakuin University in Kofu, Japan. == Career == Go won a bronze medal in the 500m at the 2017 Asian Winter Games. She competed in the women's 1000 metres and will also compete in the women's 500 metres at the 2018 Winter Olympics.
